Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:06.82,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,It was only a small pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:11.11,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Feelings that were supposed to have connected were blocked,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.54,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,unable to reach the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:17.89,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Wishes get tangled up,\Nhearts and hopes melt together...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:20.50,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,We almost lose sight of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:25.87,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Now matter how sad the past,\Nno matter how dark the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:28.54,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Still, we have to stand up against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:33.12,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Because I'm sure that everyone is fighting at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:40.00,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha A's{\i1}\Nwill now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:50.68,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Prayers echoing in the vast skies turn to miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:13.64,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Teardrops melt and flow into the blue of the middle of the night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:19.82,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,I met a warmth that engulfs all without hesitation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:22.85,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Just like the pure white snow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.92,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Words that are honest no matter how far you go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:32.80,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,It moves me as I wear wings of steel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:38.33,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Each time I am hurt,\NI can become kinder
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:46.77,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,My only wish is to protect that smile of yours to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:53.82,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Memories of sadness engraved across the ages
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:02:00.16,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,You are an angel of light, catching them straight on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:05.96,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,An eternal blaze that stopped in my heart that day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:09.43,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Releasing the deep darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:15.80,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,It opens the door of freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:22.73,Nanoha OP,,0,0,0,,Towards the strong, boundless future
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:43.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Though Fate's Linker Core\Nis severely damaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,her life is not in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:48.13,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Just like what happened to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:50.77,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0} absorbed it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.80,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it was while the {\i1}Arthra{\i0} was running.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:56.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We were able to help her out much faster than in your case, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:00.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,A while after the two of you departed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:04.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,the security systems at headquarters were hacked and taken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:08.32,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That was why I couldn't give commands or even contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:11.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, it's my responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:14.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Because you got the system back up quickly, Amy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:20.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,you were able to contact the {\i1}Arthra{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:23.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,And we were able to grab\Nclear footage of that masked man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:25.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:30.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Their equipment is of the same system as used by the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:34.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone out there that can crack into it from the outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:41.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Getting past all firewalls and alarms to take the system down so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:44.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's just unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:47.02,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm shifting the units around right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but I have to think of a stronger way of blocking them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:53.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that they have that good an engineer over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.71,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps they have\Nan organization to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What I also heard from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:02.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The conditions, and how they interact with each other, are still unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:03.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,By the time I got there,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:08.68,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,the masked man was already nowhere in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.68,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But she...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Signum was holding on to Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:18.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She said she had no excuse, but she wanted to relay that she was sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Allex, any problem with the {\i1}Arthra{\i0} cruising about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:22.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,No problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:26.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then, this is a bit earlier than scheduled,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:28.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but we will return to\Ncommand HQ aboard the {\i1}Arthra{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.27,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,All hands, back to your regular positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:30.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:34.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Miss Nanoha, you need to go back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If it's about Fate, then it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.80,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We'll take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.46,0:04:50.49,Nanoha A's Title1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\blur0.5\frx-30\pos(476,547)\bord0}The Heartbreaking Decision and the Courageous Choice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:50.49,Nanoha A's Title1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\blur4\frx-30\pos(476,547)\c&H901E38&}The Heartbreaking Decision and the Courageous Choice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:57.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So, we can say that we were saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,At the least, it is certain that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:02.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,he wants the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0} to be completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:06.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he wants to use the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0} once it is completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That can't be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:11.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I mean, even if he took the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0} after it's completed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,only our master can use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:17.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,At the point of completion, the {\i1}Meister{\i0} will have absolute power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:21.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There is no way threats or brainwashing would have any effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:25.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, we have heavy security around the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:30.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so I don't think there's any chance a threat will come for Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:31.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Just to be on the safe side,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:35.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Shamal, stay by our {\i1}Meister'{\i0}s side as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hey, when we finish the{\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:41.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and Hayate becomes\Nour master for real,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:45.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,it's going to make\NHayate happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:46.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What's this, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:49.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Meister{\i0} of the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i0}\Nwill have grand powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:53.70,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We, the guardians, know that better than anyone else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:57.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:01.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I think somehow we're forgetting something really important...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.28,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE1E1E1&}Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:47.09,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate! Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:50.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The hospital... an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.78,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE1E1E1&}Don't move her. Leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:53.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:04.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate, are you awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:07.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Commodore Lindy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:15.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Arf?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:19.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Arf has been at your side all night as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:22.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.64,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You're aboard the {\i1}Arthra{\i0} right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:28.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You were attacked from behind during your battle in the desert,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.26,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and had been unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:33.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Your Linker Core got absorbed a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:35.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but they say you will be fine soon.\NNo need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:38.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I was defeated, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:41.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Not even Bureau searchers could confirm this ambush beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so there's nothing you could have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. Did you not like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,No... It's not that\NI didn't like it... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:54.64,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You seemed to be having a nightmare, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:57.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But thank goodness you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:03.46,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I contacted the school and told them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:05.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,that you will be absent due to family matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,so you should rest a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You're getting hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:15.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll bring a light meal and a drink.\NWhat would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:17.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:21.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well... I'll leave it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:34.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.60,Nanoha Sign,,0,0,0,,{\t(\fscx105\fscy105)\fax-0.3\frz20.91\move(332,250,322,242,40,2001)}Uminari University Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, you seem to be all right. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes... thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:47.59,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's why I said I got a bit dizzy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:52.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and pulled the muscles in my chest and hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:55.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Geez, everyone is making such a big deal out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:58.62,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But you did hit your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:01.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Had it been something, it would have been a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.00,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, since you came out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:08.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I would like to do a few tests, so relax here for a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:13.74,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Now, Ms. Signum and Ms. Shamal...\NA word over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:15.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:22.59,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Nothing's showing up in the tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:26.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but I don't think it's just a pulled muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:29.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes. She seemed to be in great pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:32.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the paralysis is starting to spread again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:35.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She didn't have symptoms like this in the past, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.68,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I don't think she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:41.97,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But Hayate always hides all of her pain and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:44.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There is no guarantee that she won't have another seizure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:47.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It would be best for her to be hospitalized for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:48.68,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,just to be on the safe side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:51.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:54.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:57.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hospitalized?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.74,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, apparently so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, but it's just for testing to be on the safe side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So you have nothing to worry about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:13.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well, that in itself is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:17.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But if I'm here in the hospital, who's going to cook for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:21.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We'll... we'll... manage somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:25.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's right... it will be all right... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:28.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'll come visit every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:33.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Vita, you're such a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't have to be every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to do here, so you'd get bored, Vita.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:44.99,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then I'll relax and spend a vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:47.41,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,that comes with three meals and an afternoon nap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Suzuka might be texting me and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:56.12,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, I will contact her for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:02.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then we'll go home and bring you some clothes and a few books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Do you have any requests?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.31,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What should I choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:21.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Vita?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:23.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:16.48,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:19.25,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Let me report what\NI've figured out so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:21.27,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,First of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:23.76,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i1} is not its original name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:26.08,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,According to ancient sources,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:29.07,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,its real name is {\i0}Buch der Nachthimmel.{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:32.72,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,It was a tome that travelled with its {\i0}Meister,{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:36.29,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,originally created to gather great magical technology from each land
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:38.48,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,for use as research material.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:41.86,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The use of destructive powers\Nprobably began when
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:46.90,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,the main program was rewritten\Nby one of the users over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.93,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,So people who abuse Lost Logia
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:53.00,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,to recklessly attempt to gain immense power
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.62,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,existed in the past as well as the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:59.60,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Because of that corruption,\Nthe travel function
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:03.02,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,and the automatic repair of corrupted data are running out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:06.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is that the reason behind the reincarnation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:07.55,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and the perpetual respawning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,If it's ancient magic,\Nthat much might be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:12.12,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The worst part of it all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.30,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,are the changes to its owner's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:16.98,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,If there is no gathering of power for a certain period of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:20.32,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,it starts to eat away at the owner's magical powers and potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:22.82,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,And when it's complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:25.84,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,the owner's magical powers will be used without limits,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.32,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,for indiscriminate destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:30.41,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,That is why all the owners until now have,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.58,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,right after the completion of the {\i0}Buch...{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.25,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:37.37,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What about material on methods for stopping or sealing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:39.40,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm looking up right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:42.62,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,but stopping it before it's complete will probably be very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:43.38,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:47.06,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Only one the {\i0}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i1} recognizes as the true {\i0}Meister{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:50.18,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,has administrator rights to the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:53.75,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,In other words, there is no other way to stop or change the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:58.64,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Upon forced controls from the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:02.40,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,an embedded system will absorb the {\i0}Meister{\i1} and respawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:05.54,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,That's right. That is why they say
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:09.11,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,that sealing the {\i0}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i1}\Nfor good is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.82,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It started out as\Na wholesome research book.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:13.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You know, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I also feel sorry for the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,the {\i1}Buch der Nachthimmel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.93,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is that all you've researched?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:22.08,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,At this point in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.59,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I'm still looking up all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:27.17,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,But as expected from the Infinity Library,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.38,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,it's amazing that I can find whatever I look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:33.04,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Or rather, we think you are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:35.18,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,You're so skilled at searching for stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.68,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then, I'm sorry, but I'd like you to go a bit further.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:38.74,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:39.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you as well, Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:40.85,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.58,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Lotte, take over for me in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:43.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Okay, Aria!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:44.80,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:48.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yuuno sure is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:51.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was surprised by it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:53.95,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The image of that masked man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.50,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Are you thinking about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.02,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:03.74,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,This man's abilities are amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:06.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Or rather, I think it's more like impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,These two worlds...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:10.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Even with the fastest warps,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,it would take about twenty minutes to cover this much distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:16.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But after blocking a direct hit from Nanoha's new Buster,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.79,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and cleanly initiating a long-range bind,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:23.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,he crept up behind Fate without her noticing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:25.77,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and took her down,\Nin nine minutes' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:28.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That means that he's quite adept.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:31.53,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Even I couldn't manage that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:32.80,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What about you, Lotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:35.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, no way. Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:38.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm not that good at long-range magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:42.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You two clearly divide your duties, with Aria in charge of magic
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:44.56,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and you in charge of physical stuff, right, Lotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.37,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:50.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That got me into so much trouble in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:53.80,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It made you all the stronger, right?\NYou have to thank us for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:06.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:10.07,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit uneasy about not being able to use magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.74,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but physically, I'm all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:16.07,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,For the time being, Nanoha, until we're called out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:18.58,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,they want us to live quietly over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:21.83,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I guess it's like we're on standby?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:24.68,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Yeah. They're going to increase the number of armed operatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:26.84,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,and switch the main focus\Nto pursuit research.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:29.34,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hospitalized?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:37.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:40.47,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I received a call late yesterday afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:43.00,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She didn't seem to be that bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:46.33,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but apparently there are a lot of tests, so it will be a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:48.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:53.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Then how about all of us go together to visit her after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:54.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.92,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,She's your friend, right, Suzuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:59.82,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You said you were going to introduce us to her anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:01.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's better to have a visitation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:03.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,that's a little on the merry side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:04.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.76,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I don't know about the last bit, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:08.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But I think it's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:09.80,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes... thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:17.49,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.64,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, Suzuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:35.68,Nanoha Cell,,0,0,0,,{\1a&7C&\t(\fscx110\fscy110)\fs24\blur0.7\an5\c&H817C5D&\frz10.12\move(468,186,463,161,31,8248)}Suzuka Tsukimura
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:35.68,Nanoha Cell,,0,0,0,,{\1a&7C&\t(\fscx110\fscy110)\fs24\blur0.7\an5\c&H817C5D&\frz10.12\move(407,244,392,226,31,8248)}How is Hayate doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:29.28,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Dear Ms. Shamal,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:32.05,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Greetings, this is Suzuka Tsukimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:36.76,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,I would like to visit Hayate with my friends after school today,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.90,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,but is it all right for us to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:41.48,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Suzuka is such a good girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:45.18,Nanoha Cell,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\an5\frz10.12\pos(467,192)}Suzuka Tsukimura
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:45.18,Nanoha Cell,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\an5\frz10.12\pos(404,249)}How is Hayate doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:45.18,Suzuka Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\blur0.6\an5\c&484848&\frz12.12\pos(500,460)}Please get better soon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:45.18,Suzuka Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\an5\c&484848&\fs12\frz12.12\pos(540,464)}—Suzuka
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:54.78,Suzuka Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\t(\fscx110\fscy110)\blur1.2\an5\move(511,626,514,648,35,7500)\frz1.223\c&484848&\fax0.2}Please get better soon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:54.78,Suzuka Handwriting,,0,0,0,,{\t(\fscx110\fscy110)\blur3.2\an5\frz1.223\c&484848&\fax0.2\fs32\move(640,661,655,689,35,7500)}—Suzuka
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:50.80,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,If it is inconvenient for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:54.76,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,please show this photograph to Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.52,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:09.02,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What's this about Testarossa\Nand her group?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.28,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:14.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Testarossa and Nanoha,\Nthose two mages from the Bureau,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,are going to come visit Hayate today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:19.03,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Because they're friends with Suzuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:22.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, what should we do, what should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:22.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE1E1E1&}No, calm down, Shamal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.64,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, most of\NMistress Hayate's magical potential
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:27.44,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,is within the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:29.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Unless they give her detailed tests,\Nthey can't find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:32.84,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That may be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:36.63,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,In other words, we just have to be careful that we don't bump into them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:40.58,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It was a mistake to let them see my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:44.38,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When went to fight them, I should have used transformation magic or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,There's no use regretting things now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:50.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,When her friends are visiting, we can step out of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:51.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:57.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,And we'll ask {\i1}Meister{\i0} Hayate and\NDr. Ishida not to mention our names.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:01.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Would Hayate think that was weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We have no other choice.\NI'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:07.60,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\an5\pos(490,479)\c&H8A8B8D&\fax0.1\frz354.4}Hayate Yagami
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:09.37,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:12.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:18.72,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hello! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.19,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:21.98,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:24.00,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:26.22,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, everyone, sit down, sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.87,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:29.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,The coat rack is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:31.40,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.61,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Here, this is a cake from our place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.17,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's really tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:40.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Ms. Shamal, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:44.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, well... I just got a bit worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:47.85,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,You can just go inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Or is that a taboo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:59.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,This may be a strange way of putting it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.83,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but as Hayate's primary doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:03.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I really am thankful to all of you, Ms. Shamal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:05.90,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Ever since you all started living with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:08.42,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate seems so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:14.28,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Hayate's illness is very difficult to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:17.15,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But we are doing everything we can to combat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:17.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:20.88,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Hayate is the one who is facing the toughest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:24.39,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But, with all of you and all her friends supporting her,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.64,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she will get\Nsome courage and vitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:29.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So please keep supporting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:33.04,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,So that Hayate will be able to fight against her illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:37.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:45.54,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I hope Hayate gets well soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:47.51,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yes, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:51.52,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,How was your friends' visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.65,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all of them were good girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:54.89,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:56.66,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,They said they'd swing by every so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:58.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:58.69,0:21:01.73,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But you know, it's almost Christmas!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:59.10,0:20:59.68,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\t(\fax0)\fax-0.2\blur0.5\an5\c&HAADAB8&\b1\i1\3c&H6BA562&\fs64\frz342.4\move(525.667,718,442,495,33,575)}Christmas Days{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.10,0:20:59.68,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\t(\fax0)\fax-0.2\blur0.5\an5\c&H6BA562&\b1\i1\3c&H6BA562&\bord4.0\fs64\frz342.4\move(525.667,718,442,495,33,575)}Christmas Days{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:20:59.68,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\t(\fax0)\fax-0.2\blur0.5\an5\c&H446D4C&\b1\i1\3c&H446D4C&\bord6.0\fs64\frz342.4\move(525.667,718,442,495,33,575)}Christmas Days{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.76,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\an5\c&HAADAB8&\b1\i1\3c&H6BA562&\fs64\frz342.4\\pos(417,453)}Christmas Days{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.76,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\an5\c&H6BA562&\b1\i1\3c&H6BA562&\bord4.0\fs64\frz342.4\\pos(417,453)}Christmas Days{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:01.76,Nanoha Dialogue2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\an5\c&H446D4C&\b1\i1\3c&H446D4C&\bord6.0\fs64\frz342.4\\pos(417,453)}Christmas Days{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:04.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,This will be my first Christmas together with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.86,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I hope I can get out of here by then
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:08.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,and have a great, fun time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:11.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's right... it would be nice if you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:36.79,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The speed with which\Nthe {\i0}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:38.72,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,is infiltrating into Hayate seems to be steadily increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:41.72,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,At this rate, she'll only last a month at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:45.74,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,No, perhaps not even that long!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:56.11,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Something is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:22:00.28,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,My memory is telling me that this isn't the way it's supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:05.81,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,But this is the only thing we can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:12.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We'd hate it if Hayate stopped laughing... or even died... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:12.53,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:12.53,Nanoha Device2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(476,647)}Ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.47,0:22:21.34,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, Eisen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:22.83,Nanoha Device1,,0,0,0,,Explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:28.21,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Gigant{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:28.21,Nanoha Device2,,0,0,0,,{\i0\b1}Giant{\i1\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:32.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Crush it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:45.06,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:49.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's not healthy for you to work so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:50.67,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:51.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Oh, Liese...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:53.18,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,How are things going?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:55.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's going bit by bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:57.24,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Chrono's group is doing their best,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:23:01.08,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,but they are facing the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit,{\i0} so it won't be so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:02.91,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:05.36,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:08.14,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,getting you involved in this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.14,0:23:10.16,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:12.69,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,We are your familiars, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.69,0:23:15.43,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Your wish is our wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.12,0:23:18.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.10,0:23:20.60,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Durandal is already complete too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:22.20,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Sealing the {\i1}Buch der Dunkelheit...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:24.57,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that it will be fine this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:30.10,Nanoha Dialogue1,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:40.51,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I won't forget even when I grow up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.51,0:23:48.44,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My love, the day that we came across each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:53.22,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,In this place, where flowers bloom intensely
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.22,0:23:56.93,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I kept you in tears
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:24:00.33,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I remember the promise
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:06.79,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My love, the smile that I love so much
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:17.44,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,That day, when the secret door opened
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:24.88,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I was chasing after a small white butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.23,0:24:33.13,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I got lost, and I wanted to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.13,0:24:36.87,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My true wishes, my true feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.87,0:24:41.37,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Maybe you taught those to me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.37,0:24:45.51,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,Guarded by such kind feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.51,0:24:49.08,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I was spoiled for all this time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.08,0:24:52.88,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,How you thought dear of me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.88,0:24:58.85,Nanoha ED,,0,0,0,,My love, I won't forget all of you
