Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.38,0:25:11.48,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The {\i0}Buch der Dunkelheit{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.48,0:25:13.83,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,is almost complete,\Nbut then {\i0}that{\i1} happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.83,0:25:17.24,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Was it coincidence or necessity,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.24,0:25:19.70,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,or even destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.70,0:25:23.12,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,The time that had stopped is now running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.12,0:25:26.34,Nanoha Narration1,,0,0,0,,Next episode of\N{\i0}Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha A's:{\i1}
